OL,3,CRedknapp or Mourinho 'could turn Spurs
OL,4,Cround', says Chris Kamara
OL,6,FFormer football manger and
OL,7,Fprofessional player Chris Kamara said
OL,8,FSpurs needed someone like Harry
OL,9,FRedknapp or Jose Mourinho to turn the
OL,10,Fclub around after Igor Tudor left the
OL,11,Fnorth London side.
OL,13,FKamara, who now works as a Sky Sports
OL,14,Fpundit, said Tottenham needed a
OL,15,Fmanager with experience after parting
OL,16,Fways with Tudor who had never managed
OL,17,Fin the Premier League.
OL,19,FTottenham are just one place and one
OL,20,Fpoint above the relegation zone.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G1/7
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
