CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F402A1774887079
OL,3,CRedknapp or Mourinho 'could turn Spurs
OL,4,Cround', says Chris Kamara
OL,6,F"What the club needs is a lift,"
OL,7,FKamara told ITV News London.
OL,9,F"They tried the young with not that
OL,10,Fmany games under their belts managers
OL,11,Fso they've been through them, so why
OL,12,Fnot try Harry Redknapp or Jose
OL,13,FMourinho, just somebody who could come
OL,14,Fin and give the place a massive lift.
OL,16,F"Their supporters would love it!
OL,18,F"Imagine Josie walking down the lane
OL,19,Fand onto that new stadium with all
OL,20,Fthose fans behind - that would be
OL,21,Ficonic," Kamara explained.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/7
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
