PN,40203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F402A1774887079
OL,3,CRedknapp or Mourinho 'could turn Spurs
OL,4,Cround', says Chris Kamara
OL,6,FTudor suffered five defeats from seven
OL,7,Fgames including four in a row at the
OL,8,Fstart of his reign at Tottenham.
OL,10,FThe most recent defeat came at home to
OL,11,FNottingham Forest on March 22 prior to
OL,12,Fthe international break.
OL,14,FTudor's exit leaves Spurs without a
OL,15,Fhead coach heading into the final
OL,16,Fseven games of the Premier League
OL,17,Fseason and facing the prospect of
OL,18,Frelegation.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G3/7
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,403,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F402A1774887079
OL,3,CRedknapp or Mourinho 'could turn Spurs
OL,4,Cround', says Chris Kamara
OL,6,FKamara added: "There is a way back if
OL,7,Fthey go down - of course there is. But
OL,8,Finitially they need to stabilise the
OL,9,Fclub and say let's get a short term
OL,10,Fmanager, someone with experience who's
OL,11,Fbeen through that situation, like Roy
OL,12,FHodgson at Bristol City.
OL,14,F"Now people look at his age and think
OL,15,Fwhy are you doing it?
OL,17,F"They do it because of the love of the
OL,18,Fgame, not for the money. And those
OL,19,Ftwo, Harry and Joe, they would
OL,20,Fobviously want to get paid, but they
OL,21,Fwould save that club."
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G4/7
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
