OL,3,CRedknapp or Mourinho 'could turn Spurs
OL,4,Cround', says Chris Kamara
OL,6,FFormer Brighton boss Roberto De Zerbi
OL,7,Fand ex-Burnley and Everton manager
OL,8,FSean Dyche are among the bookmakers'
OL,9,Ffavourites to take over, or they could
OL,10,Fturn to Ryan Mason, boyhood Spurs fan
OL,11,Fand player who has twice been
OL,12,Fcaretaker before.
OL,14,FAnother man linked with the role, Adi
OL,15,FHutter, appeared to distance himself
OL,16,Fon Sunday evening from any suggestion
OL,17,Fhe would take up the reins for the run-
OL,18,Fin.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G6/7
